<div class="title">
<h2 itemprop="headline">Is the UN Preparing for the &#8220;Second Covid Lockdown&#8221;? Oppressive Measures Worldwide, Obedience and Acceptance&#8230;</h2>
<h3 class="subtitle">Globalized fearmongering. It fits an agenda, a huge sinister agenda</h3>
<div class="meta">
<div class="post-info">
<div class="author">By <a href="https://www.globalresearch.ca/author/peter-koenig" title="Posts by Peter Koenig">Peter Koenig</a></div>
<div class="grDate">Global Research, September 08, 2020</div>
</div>
<div class="catAndTag">
<div class="cats">Region: <a href="https://www.globalresearch.ca/region/europe" rel="tag">Europe</a></div>
<div class="cats">Theme: <a href="https://www.globalresearch.ca/theme/intelligence" rel="tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="https://www.globalresearch.ca/theme/science-and-medicine" rel="tag">Science and Medicine</a>, <a href="https://www.globalresearch.ca/theme/united-nations" rel="tag">United Nations</a></div>
</div>
</div>
